      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled distinction. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, reflecting a standard of care that transcends the ordinary. Every surface and mechanical component has been meticulously preserved, offering an ownership experience indistinguishable from a showroom delivery. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of excellence, this represents a premier acquisition opportunity.",
